snippet: Ireland produced the first major upset of the Cricket World Cup with a dominant four-wicket win over the West Indies, a two-time champion, in Nelson, New Zealand.
abstract: Ireland defeats West Indies by four wickets with 25 balls to spare in Cricket World Cup.
lead_paragraph: Ireland produced the first major upset of the Cricket World Cup with a dominant four-wicket win over the West Indies, a two-time champion, in Nelson, New Zealand.

headline.main: Ireland Upsets West Indies at Cricket World Cup
